# Imported tuple collection pipeline

```scalascript
def importedTupleReport(names: List[String], grades: List[Int]): List[String] =
  val pairs = names.zip(grades)
  val first = pairs.head
  val second = pairs.tail.head
  val third = pairs.tail.tail.head
  val selected = s"${first._1}:${first._2}"
  val matched = second match
    case (name, grade) => s"$name=$grade"
  val nested = Some(third) match
    case Some((name, grade)) => s"Some($name/$grade)"
    case _ => "missing"
  List(selected, matched, nested)
```
